{"tid":668100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國體操隊醫性侵332人 涉事大學賠39億和解","createTime":"2018-05-17T10:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T11:09:11.000Z","uid":153228,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"6360f20c3164dbfdea7bb33e34b6d0afb2784b07","tid":668100,"uid":153228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:23:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/718012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F718012&d=EJiCHVrPimDYvebvO0lo5kkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=17822ac8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F718012&h=7cf22eba\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/718012</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180517/_2018051711131869587_detail.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180517%2F_2018051711131869587_detail.jpg&h=6ef76c7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n54歲的美國體操國家隊前隊醫納薩爾，涉嫌性侵少女，他的前僱主密西根州立大學與被害人達成和解。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n54歲的美國體操隊前隊醫納薩爾（Larry Nassar），涉嫌性侵運動員達20年，被重囚終身，曾聘請他為校隊服務的密歇根州立大學（Michigan State University）宣布，同意與332名遭受性侵的女受害者賠償以達成和解，賠償金額共逾5億美元（約39億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n據外媒報道，律師曼利（John Manly）在聯合聲明中表示，該項協議要求學校向當前訴訟中的332名受害者支付4.25億美元。另外，還會撥出一筆7,500萬美元給信託基金，以便賠償予還沒曝光的受害者。這項歷史性的解決方案，是由拒絕沉默、勇敢站出來的300多名女性的勇氣所爭取得來的。<br />\n<br />\n納薩爾今年1月就20多年來的性侵案認罪，被判處入監40至175年，法官還在法庭上表示「你不配再從監獄走出來」。納薩爾的性侵對象不乏多名美國奧運國家隊選手，其中還包含奧運體操金牌得主拜爾絲（Simone Biles）、瑪羅妮（McKayla Maroney）、道格拉斯（Gabby Douglas）和拉絲曼（Aly Raisman），以及2000年雪梨奧運體操銅牌丹徹爾（Jamie Dantzscher）。"},{"pid":"0d133f17809e0eb30873f03288a68df0226c0459","tid":668100,"uid":118480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:25:57.000Z","msg":"暗黑新體操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e731992a72ac9e2628391f2cb48799870cef13e","tid":668100,"uid":83251,"like":21,"dislike":20,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:25:58.000Z","msg":"被人屌下就有咁多億，好賺過做雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5fd192e19ff897228d96d4f4dbef6b802450dc","tid":668100,"uid":52793,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:32:34.000Z","msg":"冇受害者圖？"},{"pid":"370df1c8b7e3bc42620045d671f876206381b097","tid":668100,"uid":158936,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:35:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26f130935860e38fd04710527c0d1d81483d437e","tid":668100,"uid":185953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:52:36.000Z","msg":"癡根 成332咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4505d96af903381397f09651a7fe95accf93938c","tid":668100,"uid":15862,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:53:58.000Z","msg":"有錢就和解 仲可以點樣唔比人話雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68de3bb8daa19cde6043f102b76389eac2107bb","tid":668100,"uid":73356,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:55:11.000Z","msg":"1個人分得百幾萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3782cfb79940308ca152e96e90b6d5761bbcaf76","tid":668100,"uid":15880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:55:42.000Z","msg":"一個一千萬<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以性侵我<br />\n我和解就得架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf905751e5e6c9f1671d3b7d7619cec69b5aa3f","tid":668100,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"370df1c8b7e3bc42620045d671f876206381b097","tid":668100,"uid":158936,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:35:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:55:52.000Z","msg":"曾經被指學校知悉事件<br />\n<br />\nThe president of USA Gymnastics, which oversees the US Olympic team, as well as the entire board of directors resigned after at least 156 women came forward to testify against the disgraced ex-doctor.<br />\n<br />\nEarlier this year, the university's president and director of athletics resigned amid claims that school officials had been told of allegations against Nassar years ago but failed to act.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-44146812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-44146812&d=EJiCHVrPimDYvebvO0lo5kkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=ee9add83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-44146812&h=2c25fac2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-44146812</a>"},{"pid":"3ac8ec55f5bae6eeaa04043516b101678468444c","tid":668100,"uid":143288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c68de3bb8daa19cde6043f102b76389eac2107bb","tid":668100,"uid":73356,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:55:11.000Z","msg":"1個人分得百幾萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:56:33.000Z","msg":"仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b360bf88047e2ac842abf0c7f75967df327d20f6","tid":668100,"uid":2337,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:57:15.000Z","msg":"332個勞資糾紛姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1287c9e8b57d5ccfc7772deef673d76487a05d7","tid":668100,"uid":82317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c68de3bb8daa19cde6043f102b76389eac2107bb","tid":668100,"uid":73356,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:55:11.000Z","msg":"1個人分得百幾萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:57:21.000Z","msg":"比隊醫摸一下胸都算性侵"},{"pid":"5c475f02e17b51f8298afdcb526780bf0c661760","tid":668100,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc